Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:04.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have 3 guests today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:06.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, that's 4 guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meaning I'm a guest too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:11.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meaning I'm a guest too?\NPlease call out the title of this show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Monthly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:15.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,ADR...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:16.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bulletin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:19.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Simoun{\i0}\N{\i1}Monthly! ADR Bulletin Special{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:23.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello! I'm Mikako Takahashi,\Nand I play Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:29.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,How do you do. I'm Rika Morinaga,\Nthe voice of Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello. I'm Kaori Natsuka,\Nand I play Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It felt like we pretty much\Nhad to do that or else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:39.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but since\Nyou were the third one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:43.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you had to be the grand finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:46.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I wasn't much\Nof a grand finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:50.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,With three guests instead of two,\Nit's pretty boisterous, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:54.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a lot more\Nboisterous than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:56.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:58.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:04.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun OX (TruelFalse) Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:06.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:06.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:06.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Time for the Simoun OX Quiz.\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Time for the Simoun OX Quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:10.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:10.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThat's what we're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:11.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what we're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, and it's self-explanatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:14.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:16.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:17.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:18.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:18.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now then...\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:18.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:19.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,...shall we begin?\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:19.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:20.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,...shall we begin?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:20.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:20.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. Here's the question!\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. Here's the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:27.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've changed somehow,{\i0}\N{\i1}playing your current character...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:28.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:29.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,True!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:30.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:33.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,False?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:34.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,False?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? I put up true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel that compared\Nto myself today...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:43.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I was much closer to\NRoatreamon when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:45.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not so much that I've changed,\Nbut that I came to realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:48.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that I might have been\Nmore like her back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:51.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I think, "You've\Ngot to grow up!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:54.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,...whenever I look at Roatreamon\Nmore and more these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:57.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,In my case, the reason\Nwhy I put up an X...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:58.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is because Yun\Nreally hates war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I've felt that\Nway for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:04.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,"It would be best not to have\Nto go into battle at all."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:07.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,That way of thinking hasn't\Nreally changed for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I can really relate to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:13.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not that I think, "I see..."\Nwhen Yun expresses her views...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's more like, "That's right."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:19.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I feel that I can say my\Nlines straight from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:21.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:22.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,How about you, Rika?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,How about you, Rika?\NNothing's changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:27.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I have the same kind\Nof personality as Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:29.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean like being mischievous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:31.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean like being mischievous?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's you being mischievous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's you being mischievous?\NI don't know if it's really mischief...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's really mischief...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but you know, like\Nplaying little jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:38.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina-jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, like playing Mamina-jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:44.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Also, like when things aren't clear,\Nshe turns around and explodes on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Come on, you!" Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right, Mamina's\Nthe type who...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:50.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,She always seems to be\Ncrackling with emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's how she's\Ndepicted in the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina is the most\Ntemperamental, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:55.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's a lot like Aer in that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:57.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're probably right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:58.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, she does seem to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, she does seem to be.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:01.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm convinced.\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, let's move on to\Nthe next question. Drum roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're 17 and you{\i0}\N{\i1}must go to the Spring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would you choose to{\i0}\N{\i1}become female after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,True!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're split...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're split...\NThis is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,An X for you, Rika!\NYou're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:23.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just want to see what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:26.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, you can't go around\Nhitting on people if you're a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if you're a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You want to hit on girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:30.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you?\NBut why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hit on girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:37.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, I want to go to the beach\Nand ask girls out like they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:38.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:41.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why? Don't you mean you\Nwant to be asked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I want to go up to an\Neasy-Iooking girl and pick her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:48.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you get\Nhit on like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what do you do? Just bare\Nyour fangs at the guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:54.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I always wonder if there are\Nthat many girls who do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and I want to check\Nit out for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean, girls who'd fall for your bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean, girls who'd fall for your bait.\NRight, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,How many girls are there who'd\Nactually be like, "Ah, sure"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think there's that many?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think there's that many?\NI don't really want to check that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:08.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Question: Do you want me as your pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait till I'm finished\Nasking the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:16.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, Oh Why!? Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:18.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:20.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's just too many of these...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...special, hard-to-memorize\NSimoun terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,So in this corner we're going to\Ntry to refresh everyone's memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:28.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Simoun-sama. If you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:32.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,What in the world\Nis a helical motor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Helical motor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Helical motor is the one we always\Ndisagree on where to put the accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:37.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:41.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it helical MOtor\Nor is it helical moTOR?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,And helical MOtor is the\Ncorrect way to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:44.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think we just\Nreviewed the wrong thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:46.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that wasn't it.\NWe need to go over its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Its meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:50.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Its meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:50.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:51.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have no idea, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard to actually\Ndefine something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't it like... the engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,The vehicle of the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:03.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...\NVehicle of the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:07.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's part of the vehicle. Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean the swirly thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:09.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,The swirl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:11.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:14.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh well, that's close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the Helical Motor?{\i0}\N{\i1}"An ancient system developed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in order to utilize the power{\i0}\N{\i1}of the deity Tempus Spatium."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if you read the answer,\Nit doesn't really register.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't register at all for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we've already been\Nthrough a lot of ADR sessions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:27.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I still haven't\Nuttered that line once yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I've said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:28.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:32.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I really, really\Ndon't get it! I never have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying\Nwhatever the script says!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,The truth comes out!\NYou just confessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never had much to\Ndo with all that, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,The power of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:42.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a system?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meaning it's a system that\Nwas built by somebody, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Long, long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:51.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's like an Intel chip or\Nsomething? I mean, what do I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:55.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you could\Nsay the nuance is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:56.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah...\NI see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,This one was a little hard to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,This one was a little hard to answer.\NIt was a hard question, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are all the questions\Ngoing to be this difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're in for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Makes you nervous about\Nthe next one, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,What, you mean that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it all right to\Nend it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems all right. So we're\Ngoing to end this corner now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:16.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,So anyway, that's it for today.\NWhy, Oh Why!? Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:22.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now then, time to\Nannounce a Simoun product.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:26.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, time for a\Nproduct announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,You won't believe this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:34.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a Simoun game will be\Ncoming out on the Playstation 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:35.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Game, game!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Game, game!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Game, game!\NGame, game!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,So tell us, what kind of\Ngame is it going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, the title is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Simoun: Battle of Thorns\N- Seal by Ri M_a_jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:44.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:45.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sounds fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sounds fierce.\NYes, for some reason it sounds fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never even heard\Nof "sealing by Ri M_a_jon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:52.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know!\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,"The recording process\Nis on a marvelous roll!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what it says here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:56.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what it says here.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is the recording going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:00.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure! I'm at the top of my game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's going well for us too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:02.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's going well for us too, right?\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:08.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,So anyway, we hope you're\Nlooking forward to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the release of this new\NSimoun Playstation 2 game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:14.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Working with you has worn me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are my lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right then...\NGood job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:23.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mmm...\NKaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,What, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really caught you off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:32.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we were told we could\Nstart off in a laid-back way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but now I'm worried if\Nthey can even use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know. I'm really worried too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:39.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,For the most part, all we really\Ndid was chat about stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:43.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. I think the editors have\Ntheir work cut out for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was like we were\Nbroadcasting the fact that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we had no knowledge of Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we had no knowledge of Simoun!\NWe came off like Simoun newbies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,We came off like Simoun newbies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even though the three of us\Nhave already done a lot of ADR.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:56.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we should have a lot more\Nadvance knowledge than everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:59.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we ended up making a\Nlot of clueless comments!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But let's not dwell on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was laid-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:03.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was a lot of fun!\NLet's do a good job recording!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, the ADR.\NLet's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:07.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, there are still a lot\Nof Simoun episodes coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so please keep watching Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please continue to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:17.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't miss the next episode!!{\i0}
